---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer - TopOnlineForm" description="Read the Disclaimer for TopOnlineForm. We are a private information portal and not affiliated with the Government of India.">
  
  <div class="bg-blue-900 text-white text-center py-12 px-4 border-b-4 border-red-600">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-wide uppercase">Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-blue-200 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase">Important Information</p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    
    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-l-8 border-yellow-500 p-6 md:p-8 rounded-r-lg shadow-sm mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-800 flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-3xl">⚠️</span> Not a Government Website
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-800 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <strong>TopOnlineForm.com</strong> is a privately owned informational website. We are <strong>NOT</strong> affiliated, associated, authorized, endorsed by, or in any way officially connected with the <strong>Government of India</strong>, any State Government, or any Government organization.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
      
      <section>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 border-b pb-2">1. Source of Information</h3>
        <p>
          The information provided on this website (recruitment news, exam dates, results) is collected from various official sources including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-3 space-y-2">
          <li>Official Government Websites (e.g., upsc.gov.in, ssc.nic.in)</li>
          <li>Official Notification PDFs</li>
          <li>Employment News Papers</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-3">
          While we strive to provide 100% accurate information, we do not claim ownership of any government logos or trademarks used on this site. They are used for informational purposes only.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 border-b pb-2">2. Accuracy & User Responsibility</h3>
        <p>
          We try our best to keep the information updated and error-free. However, mistakes can happen. 
          <strong>We strongly advise all users to verify the details from the Official Notification PDF</strong> link provided in every post before applying for any job or paying any fee.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 bg-red-50 text-red-700 p-4 rounded border border-red-100 font-medium">
          TopOnlineForm.com and its team will not be responsible for any loss, financial damage, or inconvenience caused due to any inadvertent error in the information provided.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 border-b pb-2">3. Third-Party Links</h3>
        <p>
          Our website contains links to external official websites. We have no control over the content and availability of those sites. The inclusion of any links does not imply a recommendation or endorse the views expressed within them.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 border-b pb-2">4. No Job Guarantee</h3>
        <p>
          We are an information provider, not a recruitment agency. We do not guarantee a job to any user. We never ask for money for job placement or interviews. Please be aware of fraudulent calls.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center text-sm text-gray-500 border-t pt-6">
      <p>If you have any questions regarding this disclaimer, please contact us at <a href="mailto:help@toponlineform.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">help@toponlineform.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
